- The matter's not up for discussion.

1026
01:20:20,286 --> 01:20:22,351
Drop it, hero.

1027
01:20:22,417 --> 01:20:23,385
Drop it.

1028
01:20:24,398 --> 01:20:27,167
Now walk. Easy.

1029
01:20:28,294 --> 01:20:29,928
Walk.

1030
01:20:31,720 --> 01:20:33,347
